#####Set the target shape and dimensions
#
###Cylinder######
#####sn124 dimensions#########
/Hinda/det/setTargetShape Cylinder
/Hinda/det/setTargetDiameter 1.575 in
/Hinda/det/setTargetLz 7.874 in
/Hinda/det/setTargetTheta 0 rad
/Hinda/det/setTargetPhi 0 rad
#
###Rectangle#####
#/Hinda/det/setTargetShape Rectangle
